  "notes": "## v0.1.9 — Unified settings & widget polish\n\n**New**\n- Single-page settings with all sections on one scrollable page\n- Collapsible sidebar with title bar toggle; preference is remembered\n- Custom title bar with minimize, maximize, and close controls\n- Collapsible speech model sections for local and cloud engines\n\n**Changed**\n- Settings reorganized into Getting started, Speech models, Transcription, Output, and System\n- Speaking widget with press-and-hold scale feedback and hover outline\n- Lightweight HUD event hook for faster overlay startup\n\n**Fixed**\n- Speaking widget press and drag visuals behave correctly on Windows\n- HUD position saves no longer trigger full settings reloads\n- Event listener leaks across HUD drag and model downloads\n\n**Removed**\n- LLM post-processing via local llama.cpp server",
